lbzip2 was originally written by Laszlo Ersek <lacos@caesar.elte.hu>. Version
2.0 was written by Mikolaj Izdebski <zurgunt@gmail.com>.

lbzip2 also includes some code derrived from Julian Seward's bzip2 1.0.3, some
code derrived from Mark Adler's public domain inflate.c and some documentation
derrived from Julian Seward's bzip 0.21. Finally lbzip2 includes some code and
documentation from GNU build system and Gnulib.
